[2026-03-18T18:15:01.430Z] [STDOUT] {"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_018RfZ84d9oPMBAnRg9GqP6X","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"All 5 ideas saved successfully. Here's the summary:\n\n## Feature Scout Results — Event Bus & Subscriptions\n\n**5 ideas created** and saved to Vibeman:\n\n| # | Title | Category | Effort | Impact | Risk |\n|---|-------|----------|--------|--------|------|\n| 1 | Content-based event filtering on subscriptions | functionality | 5 | 8 | 4 |\n| 2 | Dead letter queue with configurable max retries | functionality | 4 | 7 | 3 |\n| 3 | Wildcard event type subscriptions | functionality | 3 | 7 | 3 |\n| 4 | Event replay and redelivery API | functionality | 4 | 7 | 3 |\n| 5 | Event bus delivery metrics and observability | user_benefit | 5 | 8 | 2 |\n\n### Key Observations\n\n- **Event matching is simple** — subscriptions can only filter on exact eventType and sourceId prefix. No payload content filtering, no wildcards on event types. This is a gap vs. mature event buses (EventBridge, NATS, RabbitMQ).\n- **No retry ceiling** — `deferEventForRetry` has exponential backoff capped at 60s but no max retry count, so poison-pill events loop forever.\n- **No event replay** — terminal events (delivered/skipped/failed) can't be reprocessed, which is critical for debugging and recovery.\n- **Minimal observability** — health endpoint only exposes pending count and backlog age; no per-type or per-persona delivery breakdown.\n- **Existing code is reusable** — the `sourceFilterMatches` wildcard logic in `bus.ts` can be directly reused for eventType pattern matching, making idea #3 especially low-effort."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":3257,"cache_read_input_tokens":57277,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":3257},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"597c251f-1873-4ca4-81df-2d4fcccf9ef7","uuid":"a0221e02-78c7-4515-b565-39cefa118ebf"}
